&lt;p&gt;Information on biofuels statistics, including the pre-release access list, and related technical documentation &lt;a href="https://www.gov.uk/technical-guidance-for-transport-stats#biofuels-statistics"&gt;can be found here&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;

